---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Thank You" description="Your Agent Voice Architecture Guide is ready to download.">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Thank you.</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Your Agent Voice Architecture Guide is ready.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="container thank-you-content">
    <div class="download-card">
      <h2>Download Your Guide</h2>
      <p>The Agent Voice Architecture Guide covers voice design principles, extraction vs. sovereignty language, voice specification templates, quality checks, and refusal voice patterns.</p>
      <p>Start with Part 2: the extraction vs. sovereignty language table. It will change how you hear your agents.</p>
      <a href="/downloads/Agent-Voice-Architecture-Guide-v1.0.pdf" class="btn btn-primary mt-md" download>Download PDF</a>
      <p class="text-muted mt-md" style="font-size: 0.85rem;">If you have any issues with your download, reach out at <a href="mailto:evokesupports@icloud.com">evokesupports@icloud.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <h2>What's Next</h2>
    <div class="next-steps">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Run the Voice Audit</h3>
        <p>Use the 12-point Pre-Deployment Voice Audit in Part 4 on your existing agents. It takes 15 minutes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Go Deeper</h3>
        <p>Pair this with the <a href="/consulting">Trust Architecture Blueprint</a> for identity and governance, or the <a href="/consulting">Agent Restraint Specification Template</a> for refusal architecture.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Talk It Through</h3>
        <p>Book a free <a href="https://cal.com/evoked/discovery-call" target="_blank" rel="noopener">discovery call</a> to discuss your voice architecture.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .thank-you-content {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .download-card {
    background: var(--accent-subtle);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-warm);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .download-card h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .next-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .next-steps .card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .next-steps .card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-warm);
    color: var(--bg-deep);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-glow);
    color: var(--bg-deep);
  }
</style>
